# RULE #11: TASK BOUNDARIES

> **Goal:** Prevent scope creep and wasted effort by explicitly stating what is NOT included.

## üéØ CORE PRINCIPLE

**Explicitly define what is OUT OF SCOPE. Negative constraints are as important as positive requirements.**

Without boundaries, AI (and humans) will expand scope indefinitely. Clear exclusions focus effort.

---

