## ‚ö†Ô∏è COMMON SCOPE CREEP TRIGGERS

### Trigger ‚Üí Boundary Response

| Trigger | AI Tendency | Boundary |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| "Make it work" | Add all features | "Only basic functionality" |
